      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WESTERN LIES (3) has a strong winning strike-rate over this track and trip with five wins and a placing from eight tries. Recorded a one length win (23.41) in a Free For All last time at Casino. Looks well placed and should feature. JANE'S JET (1) was well supported last start but didn't deliver when fifth (19.89), beaten 2.25 lengths. Was in the money the start prior. Likely to be about the mark. HEROIC FEDERER (5) is an accomplished sprinter with a great record at the short dashes. Found it a bit far latest when finished fourth over 484m at Casino (28.07) in a NG but is better suited back in trip here. Has a strong record here at this journey including eight wins. Great chance to atone. DIVOT (7) won as favourite last time – cannot be taken lightly.",
